{"tid":1875690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】日本執政黨發動國會議員向中國捐款","createTime":"2020-02-12T02:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T03:07:34.000Z","uid":30040,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"254f63add735c09a5d4cd45330b02a557d07538c","tid":1875690,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"日本執政黨自民黨幹事長二階俊博2月10日宣布，針對中國發生的新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情擴大，將向中國提供支援資金。自民黨將從所屬的國會議員經費中，每人先扣除5000日圓（353港元），用於向中國捐款。<br />\n據《日本經濟新聞》、TBS電視台、時事通訊社等日媒報道，二階俊博2月10日在記者會上表示，針對在中國發生的新型冠狀病毒肺炎感染擴大，自民黨將向中國提供支援資金。<br />\n<br />\n二階俊博表示：「自民黨希望募集到捐款，轉交到當地。鄰居有難時，我們提供幫助是理所當然的。」<br />\n<br />\n自民黨將從黨所屬的國會議員3月的經費中，統一先行扣除5000日圓（353港元），作為捐款向中國提供援助。<br />\n<br />\n截止目前，日本國會共有710位議員，其中自民黨籍議員人數為397人，預計這次自民黨將募集到約200萬日圓（14.1萬港元）捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來日本先係真兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f72929ab2a5968b6fec093873de2ebe8a1098d7","tid":1875690,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"舊文"},{"pid":"d5b6970fd00f2d88a026a3a336165d4ff7692e38","tid":1875690,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"習近平：Good Dog<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2980194/org/35c2ec6e0a753f2eb2bd9b2ca7178a3e.JPG/c23r_aeUgVLBiohZrozVHviUOR6yI1nowTAN8sEwDfI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2980194%2Forg%2F35c2ec6e0a753f2eb2bd9b2ca7178a3e.JPG%2Fc23r_aeUgVLBiohZrozVHviUOR6yI1nowTAN8sEwDfI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=5e80ca3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3829a56a7c1ab471f7deff9092f6bdfc5b66870","tid":1875690,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f72929ab2a5968b6fec093873de2ebe8a1098d7","tid":1875690,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"舊文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"遲左少少<br />\n<img src=\